  "format": "Sean, Amanda, and Chris review '28 Years Later,' the Danny Boyle and Alex Garland reunion 23 years after '28 Days Later.' The news rundown covers the Springsteen and Bigelow trailers, the fall release-date pileup, and Tom Cruise's honorary Oscar.",
  "segments": [
