          "title": "A House of Dynamite",
          "year": 2025,
          "note": "Kathryn Bigelow's first film since 'Detroit,' scripted by Noah Oppenheim. A missile is launched at the U.S. and no one knows the source. Idris Elba, Rebecca Ferguson, Tracy Letts. Netflix, October 24."
